  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The scope of the validation plan is applied at the vehicle level, the integration item can include E/E systems,&#xD;
    software, hardware, elements of other technologies of external measures.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The information making up the validation plan should be detailed and include information relating to the configuration&#xD;
    of the item and its calibration data. And the specification of the validation test procedures, test cases, driving&#xD;
    maneuvers, the equipment, environmental conditions and acceptance criteria.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
  <purpose>To ensure that a plan is in place to validate at the vehicle level.</purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
